  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Soak bamboo skewers in water for at least 30 minutes.",
    "3. Thread 1-2 pieces of kabanos onto each skewer.",
    "4. Thread 1-2 pieces of peppery Filipino pork onto each skewer.",
    "5. Thread 1 piece of pineapple, onion, and tomato onto each skewer.",
    "6. Brush bamboo sauce on both sides of the kabanos and pork.",
    "7. Grill skewers for 5-7 minutes per side, or until kabanos is lightly charred.",
    "8. Brush with patis during last minute of grilling.",
    "9. Serve hot, garnished with garlic."
